---
title: Spiced Chickpeas and Spinach with Fluffy Cilantro Rice and Cucumber Raita
description: This vegetarian supper is packed with chickpeas and Indian-style spices. Fluffy rice is the perfect base for this curry and  a creamy raita brings it all together!
